DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
25940::$$$message_0223_0000_0000$$$::I'm worried about Saber; she was hurt pretty bad.::
25941::$$$message_0223_0001_0000$$$::"By the way, Saber.[lr]::
25942::$$$message_0223_0001_0001$$$::Um...are you all right? It looks like you took a real beating from Berserker."[lr]::
25943::$$$message_0223_0001_0002$$$::"Hm? As you can see, my body is back to normal.[lr]::
25944::$$$message_0223_0001_0003$$$::My wounds were severe enough to ensure defeat, but not to be fatal. I finished recovering roughly an hour after Berserker retreated."::
25945::$$$message_0223_0002_0000$$$::"What? So you're completely back to normal already?"[lr]::
25946::$$$message_0223_0002_0001$$$::"Of course. However, I am not entirely in peak condition.[lr]::
25947::$$$message_0223_0002_0002$$$::I was able to heal my wounds from Berserker's attacks, because they were rather mundane as these things go, but my wound from Lancer's Noble Phantasm is another matter.[lr]::
25948::$$$message_0223_0002_0003$$$::That spear must have been imbued with a special curse. The wounds I sustained have not completely healed."::
25949::$$$message_0223_0003_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
25950::$$$message_0223_0003_0001$$$::Not completely healed, huh?[lr]::
25951::$$$message_0223_0003_0002$$$::She doesn't look wounded, but Saber doesn't seem the type to complain about pain.[lr]::
25952::$$$message_0223_0003_0003$$$::As long as I'm fighting with Saber, it's sounding like I'll need to keep a pretty sharp eye on her well-being.::

